ad PDF</span><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu\"><a class=\"zDocsExportItem zDocsExportTopicButton\" href=\"#\" id=\"singlePdf\" role=\"button\">Save selected topic</a><a class=\"zDocsExportItem zDocsExportSubtopicsButton\" href=\"#\" id=\"pdfWithChildren\" role=\"button\">Save selected topic and subtopics</a><a class=\"zDocsExportItem zDocsExportBundleButton\" href=\"#\" id=\"wholeBundlePdf\" role=\"button\">Save entire publication</a></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicShare zDocsShareButton\" role=\"listitem\"><span aria-expanded=\"false\" aria-label=\"Share\" class=\"d-none d-lg-flex zDocsShareDialogButton\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" data-tooltip-content=\"Share\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsTopicActionsTooltip\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-share\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-share\"></use></svg></span><span class=\"d-lg-none zDocsShareDialogButton\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-share\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-share\"></use></svg>Share</span><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu\"><a class=\"dropdown-item zDocsShareButton zDocsShareEmail\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\"><span>Email Link</span></a><a class=\"dropdown-item zDocsShareButton zDocsShareLink\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\"><span>Copy Link</span></a></div></div><div class=\"zDocsFeedback zDocsFeedback zDocsTopicFeedback\" role=\"listitem\"><span aria-label=\"Feedback\" class=\"zDocsFeedbackButton d-none d-lg-flex\" data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_main_3540104\" data-toggle=\"modal\" data-tooltip-content=\"Feedback\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsTopicActionsTooltip\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-feedback\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-feedback\"></use></svg></span><span class=\"d-lg-none d-flex zDocsFeedbackButton\" data-backdrop=\"static\" data-return-focus=\"#zDocsTopicActionsMobile\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_main_3540104\" data-toggle=\"modal\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-feedback\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-feedback\"></use></svg><span class=\"zDocsFeedbackButtonText\"> Feedback</span></span></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><button aria-label=\"Show topic actions\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" id=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-ellipsis-h\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-ellipsis-h\"></use></svg></button><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu zDocsTopicActionsMobileDropdown dropdown-menu-right\"></div></div><div style=\"flex-basis: 100%; height: 0px;\"></div><ul class=\"zDocsTopicPageDetails\"><li class=\"zDocsTopicPageDate css-cinqea\">Last Updated<span class=\"css-cinqea\">Sept 17, 2024</span></li><li class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryDetailsItem\"><button class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryButton\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-topic-summary\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-topic-summary\"></use></svg>Summarize</button></li><li class=\"spacer\" role=\"presentation\"></li><div class=\"zDocsLabelWrapper\"><ul><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: Uniface\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=prod_uniface\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>Uniface</a></li><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: 10.4\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=uniface_10.4\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>10.4</a></li></ul></div></ul></header><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBody\" data-prismjs-copy=\"Copy\" data-prismjs-copy-error=\"Copy failed! Use Ctrl + C instead.\" data-prismjs-copy-success=\"Copied!\"><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBodyContent wide\" dir=\"ltr\"><div id=\"zDocsAiSummaryContaineruniface_104crg1665703529113.html\"></div><div><article class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/crg1665703529113.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/crg1665703529113.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"crg1665703529113\" role=\"article\">\n<div class=\"body conbody\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">Select a structure (a component or global ProcScript) to be opened for the\n         <span class=\"keyword wintitle\">Debugger Browser</span> window. The <span class=\"ph uicontrol\">Open Structure</span>\n      form is accessible only via the open icon in the browser’s toolbar. </p>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"crg1665703529113__p_d175568e1_d175569e1_d175570e1\">By default, the <span class=\"ph uicontrol\">Open Structure</span>\n         form presents retrieval fields for signatures for type <var class=\"keyword varname\">Component</var>, and\n         performs an automatic retrieve. (The <span class=\"ph uicontrol\">Automatic retrieve</span> check box of\n         the <span class=\"ph uicontrol\">Debugger Preferences</span> form is selected by default.)</p>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"crg1665703529113__p_d175571e1_d175572e1_d175573e1\">You can choose other structure types and enter retrieve profiles for the structures to retrieve.</p>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"crg1665703529113__section_ymq_ll3_1xb\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d179674e78\">Buttons</h2>\n<p class=\"p\">Use the following buttons:</p>\n<ul class=\"ul\" id=\"crg1665703529113__ul_tjb_nl3_1xb\">\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"crg1665703529113__li_d53501e1_d53502e1_d53503e1\"><span class=\"ph uicontrol\">Display</span>—choose whether\n               icons or details are displayed in the <span class=\"ph uicontrol\">Retrieval list box</span>. </li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"crg1665703529113__li_d53504e1_d53505e1_d53506e1\"><span class=\"ph uicontrol\">Retrieve</span>—retrieves all\n               structures matching the profiles you have entered for the <span class=\"ph uicontrol\">Structure\n                  name</span> field, or <span class=\"ph uicontrol\">Library</span> field, or both. </li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"crg1665703529113__li_d53507e1_d53508e1_d53509e1\"><span class=\"ph uicontrol\">Clear</span>—clears the entry\n               fields. </li>\n</ul>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"crg1665703529113__section_vrp_sl3_1xb\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d179674e114\">Type</h2>\n<p class=\"p\">Select a structure type (<code class=\"ph codeph\">Component</code> or <code class=\"ph codeph\">Global\n               ProcScript</code>). </p>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"crg1665703529113__p_d175592e1_d175593e1_d175594e1\">The value of the <span class=\"ph uicontrol\">Look in</span>\n            field changes to correspond to your selection.</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"crg1665703529113__section_iqb_vl3_1xb\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d179674e135\">Look in</h2>\n<p class=\"p\">Select the location in which to look for a ProcScript module in the debugger.</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"crg1665703529113__section_e4j_yl3_1xb\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d179674e145\">Subsystem/Library</h2>\n<p class=\"p\">Name of subsytem or library (or retrieve profile) from which to choose a component or\n            global ProcScript.</p>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"crg1665703529113__p_d175613e1_d175614e1_d175615e1\">For <span class=\"ph uicontrol\">Type</span>\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">Component</code>, enter the subsystem name or enter a profile for subsystems,\n            from which to choose a component.</p>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"crg1665703529113__p_d175616e1_d175617e1_d175618e1\">For <span class=\"ph uicontrol\">Type</span>\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">Global ProcScript</code>, enter the library name or enter a profile for\n            libraries, from which to choose a global ProcScript.</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"crg1665703529113__section_j4c_gm3_1xb\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d179674e172\">Structure name</h2>\n<p class=\"p\">Enter a structure name you want to open, or enter a profile for structures from which to\n            choose.</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"crg1665703529113__section_dxg_mm3_1xb\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d179674e181\">Retrieval list box</h2>\n<p class=\"p\">A list of the retrieved structures, in icon representation, or with details, depending\n            on your choice of button next to the <span class=\"ph uicontrol\">Look in</span> field.</p>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"crg1665703529113__p_d175640e1_d175641e1_d175642e1\">For a details list, to sort the list, click a\n            column header.</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"crg1665703529113__section_a4t_qgh_tcc\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d179674e195\">Debugger Browser information</h2>For more\n         information about the Debugger Browser, refer to: <a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"gjf1665702773980.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/gjf1665702773980.html\" title=\"Navigate to specific ProcScript modules in components or global ProcScript using the Debugger Browser, and use the browser to set breakpoints and watches.\">Browsing ProcScript Modules in the Uniface Debugger</a>.</section>\n</div>\n</article></main></article>\n</div></div></div><div class=\"bottomFeedback\"><div aria-labelledby=\"bottomFeedbackText\" class=\"bottomFeedbackContent\" role=\"group\"><span class=\"bottomFeedbackText\" id=\"bottomFeedbackText\">Was this topic helpful?</span><div class=\"bottomFeedbackButtonGroup\"><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_3540104\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-up\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-up\"></use></svg><span>Like</span></a><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_3540104\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-down\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-down\"></use></svg><span>Dislike</span></a></div></div></div><div style=\"position: fixed; bottom: 170px; right: 70px; cursor: pointer; transition-duration: 0.2s; transition-timing-function: linear; transition-delay: 0s; z-index: 3; opacity: 0; visibility: hidden; transition-property: opacity, visibility;\"><button aria-label=\"Scroll to top\" class=\"zDocsScrollTopBtn\" data-tooltip-content=\"Scroll to top\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsBackToTopToolTip\" id=\"zDocsScrollToTop\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-next\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-next\"></use></svg></button></div></body></html>", "text": "Open Structure Add to My Topics Add selected topic and subtopics Add Topic & Subtopics with topic head Add entire publication Watch Download PDF Save selected topic Save selected topic and subtopics Save entire publication Share Email Link Copy Link Feedback Last Updated Sept 17, 2024 Summarize Uniface 10.4 Select a structure (a component or global ProcScript) to be opened for the Debugger Browser window. The Open Structure form is accessible only via the open icon in the browser’s toolbar. By default, the Open Structure form presents retrieval fields for signatures for type Component , and performs an automatic retrieve. (The Automatic retrieve check box of the Debugger Preferences form is selected by default.) You can choose other structure types and enter retrieve profiles for the structures to retrieve. Buttons Use the following buttons: Display —choose whether icons or details are displayed in the Retrieval list box . Retrieve —retrieves all structures matching the profiles you have entered for the Structure name field, or Library field, or both. Clear —clears the entry fields. Type Select a structure type ( Component or Global ProcScript ). The value of the Look in field changes to correspond to your selection. Look in Select the location in which to look for a ProcScript module in the debugger. Subsystem/Library Name of subsytem or library (or retrieve profile) from which to choose a component or global ProcScript. For Type Component , enter the subsystem name or enter a profile for subsystems, from which to choose a component. For Type Global ProcScript , enter the library name or enter a profile for libraries, from which to choose a global ProcScript. Structure name Enter a structure name you want to open, or enter a profile for structures from which to choose. Retrieval list box A list of the retrieved structures, in icon representation, or with details, depending on your choice of button next to the Look in field. For a details list, to sort the list, click a column header. Debugger Browser information For more information about the Debugger Browser, refer to: Browsing ProcScript Modules in the Uniface Debugger . Was this topic helpful? Like Dislike"}